calculated or derived variables

Obs cline
1 * KENDALL calculate co2 from co2den using press and ta;
2 if press not in (.,0) then co2 = co2den*8.314*(ta+273.15)/press; else co2 = .;
3 * KENDALL calculate h2o from h2oden using press and ta;
4 if press not in (.,0) then h2o = h2oden/1000*8.314*(ta+273.15)/press; else h2o = .;
5 * KENDALL calculate fh2o from le and ta;
6 fh2o = le/18/(1.91846*((ta+273.15)/(ta+273.15-33.91))*((ta+273.15)/(ta+273.15-33.91)));
7 * KENDALL calculate nee;
8 nee = fc + sfc;
9 * KENDALL calculate svp_3 from ta_3;
10 svp_3=0.61121*exp((17.502 * ta_3)/(240.97 + ta_3));
11 * KENDALL calculate svp from ta;
12 svp=0.61121*exp((17.502 * ta)/(240.97 + ta));
13 * KENDALL calculate rh_3 from vp_3 and svp_3;
14 rh_3 = (vp_3/svp_3) * 100;
15 * KENDALL calculate rh from vp and svp;
16 rh = (vp/svp) * 100;
17 * KENDALL calculate vpd_3 from svp_3 and vp_3;
18 vpd_3 = svp_3 - vp_3;
19 * KENDALL calculate vpd from svp and vp;
20 vpd = svp - vp;
21 * KENDALL calculate preccum;
22 preccum = ifn(first.year, prec, sum(preccum, prec));
